snippet.title: Slendytubbies: Online horror game - Gameplay Preview
snippet.description: A gameplay preview teaser of the free online multiplayer indie game: Slendytubbies. For more information, please visit our site.  You can download Slendytubbies here: http://zeoworks.com/ for Windows PC and Mac.  Don't want to download? no worries! you can also play it on your web browser or on facebook. :)  For more information and controls click here: http://www.touchofdeathforums.com/community/index.php?/topic/130518-slendytubbies-official-release-multiplayer-support/  Enjoy!
